":98650,"uid":28220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"周圍有暖氣的話，著羽絨加防風外套，普通長袖t 加底衫，laging加 牛仔褲，普通波鞋"},{"pid":"a9e61eae31607c9f63891776bcad34b0de15bb98","tid":98650,"uid":55153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"去邊先?<br />\n日本個d室内有暖氣唔洗太多衫<br />\n長䄂底衫 長䄂厚少少面衫 大褸/羽絨<br />\n打底褲 牛仔褲<br />\n其實已經好夠暖<br />\n<br />\n-5度其實唔係太凍 自己覺得同hk 7,8度最凍個幾日差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋落兩落雪就凍好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港就成撚日冬天落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b4dbb84b6188470b948a4508f5dbc649a82339","tid":98650,"uid":21291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"答你<br />\n<br />\n我-10度同-38度 都係咁著<br />\n<br />\nMontbell 風嬲 <br />\n無印薄羽絨 <br />\nuniqlo薄衛衣 <br />\nuniqlo heattech 保暖底衫<br />\nGu 短袖底衫（純粹用黎更換）<br />\n<br />\n配件最重要，冷帽 、手套、厚襪"},{"pid":"508ca2dded6a546a7962454af5bf665b178008c8","tid":98650,"uid":55962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:26:52.000Z","msg":"我住個度最近都-5&deg;C<br />\n上身著1-2件衫（冷/恤衫加件底衫）<br />\n出面加件north face大褸<br />\n下身普通牛仔褲加boots<br />\n有時會戴冷帽<br />\n<br />\n睇你去邊，去d室內暖既地方最好著多d layers<br />\n咁樣入到去熱可以除多兩件衫"},{"pid":"1cc7d650274c687007fa1eeef875fd771d5d1999","tid":98650,"uid":53502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:36:13.000Z","msg":"咩都假 最撚緊要係對腳同塊面 好易唔夠暖"},{"pid":"61648f0e3e6b326bd5957ddba6921d5529ba7d59","tid":98650,"uid":72470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T19:40:42.000Z","msg":"冷衫冇撚用"},{"pid":"2b13c6c2deede7d4ecf2e385784c3f6e4834c575","tid":98650,"uid":54940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T01:46:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得有三樣野係必要<br />\n<br />\n1. heatech 底衫<br />\n<br />\n2. 羽絨<br />\n<br />\n3. windstopper (唔大風可以唔著)<br />\n<br />\n除左依三件, 我仲著一件polo同一件冷衫<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解樓上話冷衫無用, 我著american eagle 件冷衫係超有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下身就好睇大唔大風<br />\n<br />\n唔大風0度都可以就咁一條chino<br />\n<br />\n大風既話10度對腳一樣凍到仆街<br />\n<br />\n鞋就著厚boot<br />\n<br />\n冷帽, 頸根, 手套是常識吧"},{"pid":"b8eb7c4d741a38b2e6d955159611f9286f031a70","tid":98650,"uid":14886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T01:47:45.000Z","msg":"有暖貼其實唔洗太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17edfc49318d5b8aa9092e8a0b8a0f4de1f1824b","tid":98650,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:00:44.000Z","msg":"1件uniqlo打底<br />\n1件短袖<br />\n2件hoodie<br />\n1頂冷帽<br />\n<br />\n-8度咁著"},{"pid":"f57d7f7bcdaf5faa27b67bd1bbd723c1163d42a4","tid":98650,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"下 你班垃圾<br />\n我一件背心搞掂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1597d37a319fd68b4e4ef492f5e952c8cc3a21b3","tid":98650,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:42:08.000Z","msg":"吸汗底衫<br />\nheatech 底衫<br />\n任意面衫<br />\n大褸<br />\nheatech 褲<br />\n厚褲<br />\n厚襪<br />\n雪靴<br />\n手套 頸巾 冷帽<br />\n<br />\n成功去完北海道 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38270458124e9ceaa1f237ebb074ff107cb28ff6","tid":98650,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:44:32.000Z","msg":"乾定濕<br />\n大風定冇風"},{"pid":"b18820422045ba8bc976b06472df559631006168","tid":98650,"uid":75537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1件uniqlo打底<br />\n1件短袖<br />\n2件hoodie<br />\n1頂冷帽<br />\n<br />\n-8度咁著</blockquote><br />\n<br />\